ence\": \"When local organizers first envisioned the 2024 Games nearly 10 years ago, they had the full, two-week basketball events planned for Accor Arena, a 16,000-seat venue in Paris that is very similar to many NBA venues.\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3156, \"end\": 3167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Accor Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 3192, \"end\": 3197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.051324341783033e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3227, \"end\": 3230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.193435227230732e-27, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local organizers\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Games\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"the full, two-week basketball events\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"a 16,000-seat venue\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheCleveland CavaliersandBrooklyn Netsplayed there Jan. 11.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That changed in early 2022, with soaring Olympic costs brought on in part by the pandemic that prompted Paris organizers to nix construction of a new swimming venue.\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3404, \"end\": 3409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.05132434178303